'''隱形能力'''，或稱'''隱身能力'''，是指人能夠將自己變成[[透明|透明]]人的[[超能力|超能力]]，這是[[奇幻|奇幻]]、[[科幻|科幻]]作品常見的題材之一。

==常見設定==
透明人的身體是看不見的，但透明人本身仍然可以看見其它的物體。有些透明人即使透明也能觸碰得到，有些則不行。隱形通常被認為是最高形式的偽裝 ，因為它不顯示任何一種重要的視覺、也沒有任何頻率的電磁波譜，如無線電、紅外線、紫外線等。

在影視作品中出現時，通常會讓透明人呈現半透明的狀態，以免閱聽者完全看不到該名角色。

==科學技術==
隱形概念最早來自於John Pendry和Andrew Ward在1996年的一篇論文。2006年[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[聖安德魯斯大學|聖安德魯斯大學]]物理學家乌尔夫·雷昂哈特（Ulf Leonhardt）曾写了一篇题为《Optical conformal mapping》的论文稱“一个隐形装置应该能使光线绕过一个物体，使这个物体看起来根本不在那里。”<ref>{{cite journal | last = Pendry | first = J. B. | coauthors = D. Schurig, and D. R. Smith | title = Controlling Electromagnetic Fields | journal = Science | volume = 312 | pages = 1780−1782 | doi = 10.1126/science.1125907 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/1125907 | accessdate = 2006-08-01 | pmid = 16728597 | issue = 5781 | bibcode = 2006Sci...312.1780P | date = June 2006 | archive-date = 2010-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100215192145/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/1125907 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Leonhardt | first = Ulf | title = Optical Conformal Mapping | journal = Science | volume = 312 | pages = 1777–1780 | doi = 10.1126/science.1126493 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/1126493 | accessdate = 2006-08-01 | pmid = 16728596 | issue = 5781 | bibcode = 2006Sci...312.1777L | date = June 2006 | archive-date = 2010-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100813113141/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/1126493 | dead-url = no }}</ref>美國羅徹斯特大學的葛林利夫 (Allan Greenleaf) 提出電磁蟲洞，光線會經由別的管道傳輸，在某處消失然後在別處出現。

目前，實用的隱形裝置不存在<ref>{{cite journal | last = Nachman | first = Adrian I. | title = Reconstructions From Boundary Measurements | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-mathematics_1988-11_128_3/page/531 | journal = Annals of Mathematics | volume = 128 | issue = 3 | pages = 531–576 | format = GIF | accessdate = 2006-08-01 | doi = 10.2307/1971435 | jstor = 1971435 | publisher = Annals of Mathematics|date=November 1988}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Wolf | first = Emil | coauthors = Tarek Habashy | title = Invisible Bodies and Uniqueness of the Inverse Scattering Problem | journal = Journal of Modern Optics | volume = 40 | issue = 5 | pages = 785–792 | url = http://www.journalsonline.tandf.co.uk.proxy.lib.fsu.edu/link.asp?id=kx4xldwr2qb8beuq | accessdate = 2006-08-01 | doi = 10.1080/09500349314550821|bibcode = 1993JMOp...40..785W |date=May 1993}}</ref>，但仍有不少科學家致力於隱形技術。2006年开始，就陆陆续续的出现了很多有趣的实验。2006年，英國倫敦帝國大學的理論物理學家[[约翰·彭德里|约翰·彭德里]]和美國[[杜克大學|杜克大學]]的David Smith 、助理教授David Schurig等人提出[[隱形斗篷|隱形斗篷]]，他們以超穎材料(metamaterial, 硅纳米材料) 製造出一個可以讓微波彎曲繞道的圓柱<ref>[http://www.themoneytimes.com/articles/20080811/scientists_turn_fiction_into_reality_closer_to_make_objects_invisible-id-1032139.html themoneytimes.com,Scientists Turn Fiction Into Reality, Closer to Make Objects "Invisible"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080816035413/http://www.themoneytimes.com/articles/20080811/scientists_turn_fiction_into_reality_closer_to_make_objects_invisible-id-1032139.html |date=2008-08-16 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/top-stories/2008/08/11/secrets-of-invisibility-discovered-115875-20692852/ |title=mirror.co.uk, Secrets of invisibility discovered |accessdate=2011-09-07 |archive-date=2011-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919110702/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/top-stories/2008/08/11/secrets-of-invisibility-discovered-115875-20692852/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校研究员Xiang Zhang透過分散光的视觉效果。

[[低可偵測性技術|低可偵測性技術]]（Stealth technology），俗稱“[[隱形技術|匿蹤技術]]”，是通過特殊設計、表面材質或裝置，降低物體被偵測到的機會或縮短其可被偵測距離的科技。

